{"tid":1378463,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"Google Pay 加西瓜卡同包車問題","createTime":"2019-07-28T15:55:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T10:38:58.000Z","uid":78374,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a6dde0cc6d111f2a93a00538198673425e9bee18","tid":1378463,"uid":78374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:55:57.000Z","msg":"小弟發現日本Google Pay已經支援西瓜卡<br />\n<br />\n我見S10都支援Type-F NFC 所以想試一試<br />\n<br />\n但係無論開左日本Google AC 連埋VPN 轉埋日文 Google pay都仲係無得加西瓜卡<br />\n<br />\n有無巴打成功到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋想問我其中一日行程想去淡路島 但係果邊交通好唔方便 <br />\n<br />\n唔想2老咁辛苦 所以想包車一日遊<br />\n<br />\n但係搵過日本好多包車公司都唔到淡路島 你地有無經驗可以分享比小弟知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"596d10953c2b3b4a86c9e83eb68de8761d5deb8c","tid":1378463,"uid":78374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:25:58.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c8a27032589b756251d7162531ae4cdbc708fb1","tid":1378463,"uid":10361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:30:55.000Z","msg":"好似得日版機先有 FeliCa ？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1949296a8d4822365be9332de8b32aa7c38d674","tid":1378463,"uid":78374,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0c8a27032589b756251d7162531ae4cdbc708fb1","tid":1378463,"uid":10361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:30:55.000Z","msg":"好似得日版機先有 FeliCa ？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:38:58.000Z","msg":"但係我見S10都有支援八達通 應該都有FeliCa掛<br />\n<br />\n我估緊Google pay會唔會check你係咪日版機 有先會開比你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}